summary: Completed comprehensive testing of OmniHub multi-tool platform. Backend APIs working at 92.3% success rate. Frontend UI and admin functionality working well with proper authentication, navigation, and credit system integration. One minor backend API issue and one frontend form selector issue identified.

flaky_endpoints.issue: External 1secmail API returning non-JSON response causing parsing error
flaky_endpoints.impact: Temp Email tool fails to generate emails

ui_bugs.issue: Name input field selector not working - input[name='name'] not found

passed_tests: Admin login with correct credentials (admin@omnihub.com / Admin@123)
Admin dashboard loads with proper role and credit display (999,999 credits)
Admin navigation to Users and Credits management pages
Credit assignment form loads and displays properly
User registration creates account with 0 credits
Credit system blocks tool usage with insufficient credits (402 status)
Credit deduction works correctly after admin assigns credits
Phone Lookup tool integration with backend API
Live TV channels endpoint returns 6 channels
Usage history and admin logs functionality
Proper error handling for unconfigured services (Eyecon API)

success_percentage.frontend: 90% (most core functionality working, minor form issue)

action_item_for_main_agent: Fix temp email API error handling for non-JSON responses from 1secmail.com. Update registration form name input selector to match actual HTML structure.
